<br>
Class imbalance really affects tank classes more than any others.  All dps classes, whether melee or hybrid, stack: i.e. a rogue AND a ranger is always better for a group than just a rogue alone.  Tanking classes are another matter.  A second tank in a group is a waste of buffs.  Consequently, balance between SK's, Paladins, and Warriors is essential for fair game play.  <br>
